Description :
        Ji Xi, a young man from China and the United States, traveled through a different world to become a prince. He thought he could accomplish a career, but his father-in-law gave him to the prince of another country in exchange for 100,000 tons of resources! What kind of strange adventure will Prince Ji Xi, who wants to be the hero of the young man but holds the script of the heroine of the young man, and his overbearing prince, will embark on a strange adventure in another world?
